791
00:44:09,500 --> 00:44:10,119
Rym: Which one is this?

792
00:44:10,200 --> 00:44:14,340
Scott: There's one where there's a button that you sort of don't see if you don't look in the right area.

793
00:44:14,761 --> 00:44:16,511
Scott: And it's like you have to jump up and hit a button.

794
00:44:16,872 --> 00:44:18,340
Scott: And you won't see it because it's like in a corner.

795
00:44:18,480 --> 00:44:20,300
Rym: Oh, I saw that button, like, right away.

